How do I update this listing?




                                             Camarda Financial Advisors is based out of Fleming Island. Camarda Financial Advisors is a large advisory firm with  More than 100 clients and discretionary assets under management (AUM) of $212,835,737 (Form ADV from 2017-05-02).  Their last reported 13F filing for Q2 2017 included $93,497,000 in managed 13F securities
    and a top 10 holdings concentration of 42.14%. Camarda Financial Advisors's largest holding is PowerShares Preferred Portfolio Trust II with shares held of 944,394.  Camarda Financial Advisors has met the qualifications for inclusion in our WhaleScore system.    WhaleWisdom has at least 19 13F filings in our database for Camarda Financial Advisors. 
                                           






